{"tid":196179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵高層加薪三成至9,090萬","createTime":"2017-04-11T06:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T07:38:25.000Z","uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"773c096121a2237c61e883fb68528d258c335e16","tid":196179,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19986871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170411&amp;mobile=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19986871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170411%26mobile%3D1&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lex4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=02637711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19986871%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170411%26mobile%3D1&h=316a8746\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19986871&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170411&amp;mobile=1</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵事故頻頻但港鐵高層去年仍坐享高薪，據港鐵昨公佈年報顯示，行政總裁梁國權2016年薪酬達1,480萬元，較2015年加薪5%或70萬元。整個港鐵董事局及執行總監會成員薪酬，亦按年大升三成至逾9,000萬元。<br />\n梁國權自2015年3月才「坐正」出任行政總裁，此前他為署理行政總裁，因此其2016年薪酬按年上升，部份應是計及升職因素。梁去年收取基本薪金及津貼等為880萬元、退休金供款140萬元，另有460萬元表現掛鈎薪酬，總薪酬1,480萬元。<br />\n<br />\n核心純利按年跌13.3%<br />\n<br />\n另外，原是車務總監的金澤培去年4月升任常務總監，升職兼加薪一成，2016年全年人工920萬元。而接替錢果豐出任港鐵主席的馬時亨，則維持收董事袍金120萬元。整個港鐵董事局及執行總監會成員薪酬按年大升30.4%至9,090萬元。<br />\n港鐵去年收入為451.89億元，按年升8.4%，但核心純利為94.46億元，按年跌13.3%，主要受累於香港物業發展利潤大跌；單計鐵路業務利潤，則按年增長約4%至89.16億元。<br />\n■記者方楚茵"},{"pid":"0fcdee5ee5b375d136cf7c33cc55a7346dbbb58b","tid":196179,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"有可加可減機制嫁嘛，唔緊要啦"},{"pid":"309b5488936b82287f68ab66dca02cca272e0d89","tid":196179,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"9千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc54e0a5077bb53200e337e8808202defba6a3ea","tid":196179,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵:為表示昨日放工時間多線收皮之歉意 決定懲罰高層加薪<br />\n  <br />\n        加幅將轉嫁予明年票價  對唔閪住  唔撚好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9df33ec9fc09a546a29488fd7835ab2cdbef39","tid":196179,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵:為表示昨日放工時間多線收皮之歉意 決定懲罰高層加薪<br />\n  <br />\n        加幅將轉嫁予明年票價  對唔閪住  唔撚好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2f73d466b46219b51acf08a864f13c28c13375","tid":196179,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"其實港鐵高層有d咩做?<br />\n<br />\n賣八達通資料？<br />\n<br />\n計下加幾多賺最多？"},{"pid":"c5c1abef51850d3ad5e4844d0def4a53b421fbf7","tid":196179,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe34b8ba8971b10cdbad2b07f94629a1baf637e","tid":196179,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實港鐵高層有d咩做?<br />\n<br />\n賣八達通資料？<br />\n<br />\n計下加幾多賺最多？</blockquote><br />\n同其他大老闆飲茶打golf攬女隊酒傾吓點樣利益輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申鳩估"},{"pid":"27a867fd525eae2ef217